  21:../../libDaisy/src/per/adc.h **** 
  22:../../libDaisy/src/per/adc.h **** /** @brief   Configuration Structure for an ADC Channel 
  23:../../libDaisy/src/per/adc.h ****  *  @details This can be used to configure a a single input, 
